{"id": "ChIJfZ42taS5woARHm4i4UpXv3Y", "rating": 4, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 148, "displayName": {"text": "3CAT Handcrafted Beverage", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJfZ42taS5woARHm4i4UpXv3Y/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVIwMHhRM1Z2UzNsNk9XTmxVRlZmUnpSMGJGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "2/19/2026 - I enjoyed drinks at this brand shop, where high-quality ingredients like fresh fruit are used.\n\nToday, I repeat the same two drinks again - handmade MANGO MOCHI and AVOMANGO SWEET DEW in K-Town - it is so good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "2/19/2026 - I enjoyed drinks at this brand shop, where high-quality ingredients like fresh fruit are used.\n\nToday, I repeat the same two drinks again - handmade MANGO MOCHI and AVOMANGO SWEET DEW in K-Town - it is so good!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jeremy L", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115138562580402046968/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKG-9NKjP_5uNkedmeTU9B8USZ0mTOVhrO0uXNTY1SUdkzEVA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-20T00:58:21.715804141Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVIwMHhRM1Z2UzNsNk9XTmxVRlZmUnpSMGJGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pVNVIwMHhRM1Z2UzNsNk9XTmxVRlZmUnpSMGJGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9a4b5369e7d:0x76bf574ae1226e1e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfZ42taS5woARHm4i4UpXv3Y/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWUVgyWkVhR281T1dsV1JrMVlWRXhMUjFKbWNYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Let's start with the drink- I tried their special mango mochi signature beverage. The mochi and mango had great flavoring but it mainly consisted of ice. It was mostly what i tasted. Not so great.\n\nDid I mention that I waited 41 min for my drink? The place was packed. The lady in the front said that they do make the drinks in order but in batches. They made my batch ( I saw my drink with my name) 20 min in and I watched it sit there for another 20 min. I told the lady that the batch has been sitting there but she kept pushing out newly made drinks because they were being placed in front of her instead of pushing out the ones who were made earlier that was placed farther out. She ignored me along with another staff member. Worst customer service at a tea shop place I ever had.\n\nThe drink was not even made well to begin with. Not worth it. The place was also not the cleanest.\n\n3cat has uniquely flavored drinks but that's it. 40+min wait is shockingly not worth it", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Let's start with the drink- I tried their special mango mochi signature beverage. The mochi and mango had great flavoring but it mainly consisted of ice. It was mostly what i tasted. Not so great.\n\nDid I mention that I waited 41 min for my drink? The place was packed. The lady in the front said that they do make the drinks in order but in batches. They made my batch ( I saw my drink with my name) 20 min in and I watched it sit there for another 20 min. I told the lady that the batch has been sitting there but she kept pushing out newly made drinks because they were being placed in front of her instead of pushing out the ones who were made earlier that was placed farther out. She ignored me along with another staff member. Worst customer service at a tea shop place I ever had.\n\nThe drink was not even made well to begin with. Not worth it. The place was also not the cleanest.\n\n3cat has uniquely flavored drinks but that's it. 40+min wait is shockingly not worth it", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Chloe Chanel", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106260253867661172181/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPAEfk6B30PKDEWO-QpFLaT33Af0wWqtN76t3ka7vjg_7GVz2Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-12T22:40:21.941633287Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWUVgyWkVhR281T1dsV1JrMVlWRXhMUjFKbWNYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWUVgyWkVhR281T1dsV1JrMVlWRXhMUjFKbWNYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9a4b5369e7d:0x76bf574ae1226e1e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJfZ42taS5woARHm4i4UpXv3Y/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxUU5HRjVkWGx1TFhabFkwbFBUbGN3TTNsZlFtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "I see that a lot of their little statues in cafe as many little fat cats do look cute but many of them wear “neck bells” which are harmful for cats nervous systems. Please educate yourself, do your research and don’t make your cat wear a bell even if it’s not a real cat do not need to normalise it. Thank you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I see that a lot of their little statues in cafe as many little fat cats do look cute but many of them wear “neck bells” which are harmful for cats nervous systems. Please educate yourself, do your research and don’t make your cat wear a bell even if it’s not a real cat do not need to normalise it. Thank you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alina Shialli", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111254017415829169221/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBiV1mqbfPMQlSeQ_LjYHsYUfdpkqGBjjrpv0Y6c1VBVZ-kl2HOA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-23T17:39:14.776973947Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxUU5HRjVkWGx1TFhabFkwbFBUbGN3TTNsZlFtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodH